ðŸ“˜ SentinelAI Bot API Documentation
API Information
Title: SentinelAI Bot
Version: 0.1.0
Base URL: http://127.0.0.1:8000
Authentication Endpoints
POST /auth/register
Register a new user.
Request Body (JSON):
{
  "username": "string",
  "password": "string"
}
Response: 200 OK
POST /auth/login
Login with existing user credentials.
Request Body (x-www-form-urlencoded):
grant_type: password
username: string
password: string
(optional: scope, client_id, client_secret)
Response: 200 OK
{
  "access_token": "string",
  "token_type": "string"
}
Bot Endpoints
POST /api/bot/api/bot/run-bot
Run the trading bot with broker credentials.
Request Body (JSON):
{
  "broker_login": "string",
  "broker_password": "string",
  "server": "string"
}
Response: 200 OK
GET /api/bot/api/bot/status
Get the current status of the bot.
Response: 200 OK
GET /api/bot/api/bot/example
Get example response or usage of the bot.
Response: 200 OK
Error Responses
HTTP 422 Validation Error:
{
  "detail": [
    {
      "loc": ["field"],
      "msg": "error message",
      "type": "error type"
    }
  ]
}
